Post.title: 一些个人常用的网站集合
Post._content:
### Google

[Google 代码风格指南](https://google.github.io/styleguide/)

[Google 开发文档风格指南](https://developers.google.cn/style/)

[Google Noto Fonts](https://www.google.com/get/noto/#sans-hans)

[Google 开发者中文博客](http://developers.googleblog.cn/)

[Google 开源项目风格指南 (中文版)](https://github.com/zh-google-styleguide/zh-google-styleguide)

[Google Samples](https://github.com/googlesamples/?utf8=%E2%9C%93&query=)

### Python

[Napoleon Python 文档风格](https://sphinxcontrib-napoleon.readthedocs.io/en/latest/)

[SPHINX Python 文档转换工具](http://www.sphinx-doc.org/en/master/)

### Android

[Gradle](https://developer.android.com/studio/build/index.html)

[Android Samples](https://developer.android.com/samples/index.html)

[Android培训课程中文版](http://hukai.me/android-training-course-in-chinese/)

### .NET

[.NET Framework 源码](https://referencesource.microsoft.com/)

[.NET 类在不同版本下的区别](https://apisof.net/catalog)

[.NET Standard](https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-cn/dotnet/standard/net-standard)

[.NET Core](https://github.com/dotnet/core)

[nuget](https://www.nuget.org/)

[.NET 在线编译器](https://dotnetfiddle.net/#)

[BenchmarkDotNet](http://benchmarkdotnet.org/)

### 图标

[IcoMoon](https://icomoon.io/)

[https://icons8.com/](https://icons8.com/)

### TensorFlow

[从源代码安装 TensorFlow](https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_sources)

[Deep Learning 中文翻译](https://github.com/exacity/deeplearningbook-chinese)

[TensorFlow 官方网址](https://www.tensorflow.org/)

### 素材

[https://pxhere.com/](https://pxhere.com/)

### 其他

[在线画图](https://go.gliffy.com/go/html5/launch)
